    "Crowdsourcing platforms can engage diverse demographics at scale to collect preference data from real-world environments.",
    "Mobile apps can facilitate longitudinal tracking of preferences over time.",
    "On the other hand, biosensors could provide real-time physiological measurements, such as salivary biomarkers during food consumption, offering objective data to complement subjective feedback.",
    "Taste-matrix complexity represents a significant challenge in gustatory research.",
    "Unlike simple chemical profiling, flavor perception is shaped by the combined effects of multiple compounds interacting within the taste matrix."
